<text top="1488" left="236" width="495" height="65" font="font8" id="p1_t8" reading_order_no="7" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">here  has  been  plenty  of  dis- </text>
<text top="1545" left="142" width="584" height="57" font="font9" id="p1_t9" reading_order_no="8" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">Tesen  over  the  last  several </text>
