<text top="1650" left="142" width="603" height="57" font="font9" id="p1_t11" reading_order_no="10" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">called  “the  software  crisis.”  Those </text>
<text top="1701" left="140" width="576" height="58" font="font10" id="p1_t12" reading_order_no="11" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">who  speak  of  such a  crisis  claim </text>
