<text top="1807" left="142" width="539" height="55" font="font12" id="p1_t14" reading_order_no="13" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">over  budget,  behind  schedule, </text>
<text top="1857" left="142" width="264" height="58" font="font10" id="p1_t15" reading_order_no="14" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">and  unreliable. </text>
<text top="1910" left="189" width="335" height="57" font="font9" id="p1_t16" reading_order_no="15" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">The  software  crisis </text>
