<text top="2015" left="140" width="492" height="58" font="font10" id="p1_t18" reading_order_no="17" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">damning  condemnation  of </text>
<text top="2061" left="140" width="480" height="65" font="font8" id="p1_t19" reading_order_no="18" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">software  practice.  The  pic- </text>
<text top="2120" left="141" width="442" height="57" font="font9" id="p1_t20" reading_order_no="19" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">ture  it  paints  is  of  a  field </text>
<text top="2167" left="141" width="481" height="63" font="font11" id="p1_t21" reading_order_no="20" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">that  cannot  be  relied  upon </text>
<text top="2223" left="141" width="473" height="58" font="font10" id="p1_t22" reading_order_no="21" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">to  produce  valid  products. </text>
<text top="2277" left="192" width="387" height="53" font="font13" id="p1_t23" reading_order_no="22" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">But  it  is  important  to </text>
<text top="2323" left="140" width="531" height="63" font="font11" id="p1_t24" reading_order_no="23" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">step  back  and  ask  some  ques- </text>
<text top="2380" left="141" width="559" height="57" font="font9" id="p1_t25" reading_order_no="24" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">tions  about  this  crisis  thinking: </text>
<text top="1487" left="815" width="564" height="63" font="font11" id="p1_t26" reading_order_no="35" segment_no="4" tag_type="text">call  the  computing  era—an  era </text>
<text top="1539" left="815" width="615" height="63" font="font11" id="p1_t27" reading_order_no="36" segment_no="4" tag_type="text">that  would  simply  not  be  possible </text>
<text top="1590" left="813" width="616" height="65" font="font8" id="p1_t28" reading_order_no="37" segment_no="4" tag_type="text">were  it  not  for  plentiful  successful </text>
<text top="2479" left="142" width="472" height="62" font="font16" id="p1_t29" reading_order_no="25" segment_no="10" tag_type="list">*  Does  it  represent  reality? </text>
